{"tid":1640342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如一齊spread呢條片去外國? 文字唔係個個都有心機睇 但片就可能會睇下","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:46:59.000Z","uid":4236,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbc18031c5bcc554b7ac17ce6d83cd434666b82","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yXTHODE24Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0yXTHODE24Q&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=ecc7520b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yXTHODE24Q</a><br />\n隔離post睇到 睇到喊曬口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經係twitter tweet左 但唔多人睇  <br />\n覺得岩外國人口味 食住NBA同暴雪個勢  順便spread埋比日本仔同韓仔<br />\n可唔可以搵twitter d人幫手spread下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求人幫手reddit開po  我會繼續係twitter tweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80af3585c504a7ad586103f7c7b53e5338042c9f","tid":1640342,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38da39336128b960cb6ac7f213cd581d70b215d1","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"無限自推"},{"pid":"0c8f397523a6181cdb9538190ae30f2d6724aab8","tid":1640342,"uid":303862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"Twitter link呢 幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9170b2b0a13867d67595624da96278e57d566c1","tid":1640342,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgNzv5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgNzv5d.jpg&h=def25fee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww8ShLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww8ShLe.jpg&h=8c7f3616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球「和尼畫」#XinniethePooh Challenge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"bd355f65a2fa84210bd09dd092fe44d14cd9bade","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"無限自推"},{"pid":"b9f5bef200ae7b091cea0915e814e6aa7c0e94d7","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"無限自推"},{"pid":"d3beec31a4ec80dbdfa8d09098d3c67ea87f8fe9","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"無限自推"},{"pid":"321b9dc28ff20584a4381c6e26b8c589fbcddd43","tid":1640342,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:37:59.00